overcome by major fangirlnesss. 
so beAUtiful....

Cause she's bittersweet, she knocks me off my feet and i can't help myself i don't want anyone else... she's a mystery she's too much for me- but i keep coming back for more...

I't 12:11 at noon. I don't why i just wrote that but i don't care it's just a given fact.  I am feeling a bit lethargic, doesn't that suck? Tommorow, "Harry and the Potters" are playing for free down-town, haven't decided if i want to go or not. I mean i've heard their c.d and i'm telling you if there was ever a time for feeling suicidal, thhat was it. There's also "Draco and the Mlafoys". That made me laugh and happy because that meant ppl were paying attention to Draco and the attention wasn't all about Pottter. God, i just sounded like a real life Slytherin, didn't i? Well....whatev. "And Proud Of It Too". lol The fact that Draco is so bloody gorgeous wasn't an excuse for how bad they sounded too. I mean there was actually a song on there that was titled "Pansy...you're my girl" (or something like that) YUCK!
Now if there was a "Draco and the Malfoys" playing, i would so go. They might hand out free posters of Draco *wishful thinking*  lol

*sigh*
...   


Am watching Edwards Scissorhands(aww), Harry potter (...the inside look- like i haven't read the damn books, please don't insult my intelligence by asuming that anything you can come up with in the movies is better than my imagination. stupid buggers, sorry just letting of some steam here). I mean everybody, the actors and whoever else that has to do with the movies are laways on interviews like :oh this year, this and this happens...BLAH BLAH BLAH. oh bloody hell, the most reason i'm mad is cause they don't talk about any of the other characters. they're always on about harry, hermione, ron...like everyone else is insignificant to the plot (which they're not). And the ammount of attention that's being paid to "THE KISS". omg, stop it already, y'know. it's not all that.
 well whatev... and am on the comp, what can i say i'm a girl- we can multi-task

i just ate like a couple of pizza and i'm tired (hence the title). oui, i mean tired, parce que je mange'd them in one standing. it was like being in a competition of who can eat the fastest. it was something like that except it was eat as much as you can they'll be finte in 2.5 secs. lol- seriously. the point is now i'm too full, my head somewhat hearts, je should be doing me homework (SHIT!), mais, i'm not. 
i don't regret it, though, mmm!. cheese and chicken pizza= awesome. it's thursday and it feels like friday, that just plain sucks.

. oh, mais, Oui. lol 'tis the truth, 'ain't it?. oh no cedric, of course i haven't forgotten about ye, i mean you. sorry still got the pirate way of talking stuck in me head. don't quite mind really.
slytherins are soo sweet-NOT, but i mean come on if someone like draco malfoy was mean to me, i'd probably curse him instead of letting him get away with it, like hermione does with the whole mud-blood shyt. sure i'd get expelled, but believe me you if she was desperate or angry- either, really- she'd come up with a way without getting caught.
Type your cut contents here.
 ofcourse i believe draco is not really evil for he would have instantly killed dumbledore, on the freaking spot, i mean. i think with his stupid way of calling 'mione mud-blood is just a habit and how come he singles her out. yeah, he hates harry and ron too but he is always single-ing hermione out. me don't have exact evidence on me lap right now, but i assure ye, there is. it's kind of like in elementary where you like someone so the little boy start bobbing the little girl on the head with a bloody ruler. getting a sort of sick satisfaction out of her incessant crying. i swear boys- the world over are a mystery to me. girls, let me tell you- yes we all dream of prince charming and/or our knight in shining armor coming to us and sweeping us into the beautiful horizon, though what we really want is the bad boys, the pirates, the rogues. the ones who look so damn beautiful it hurts and those who have the extra little smirk, that you find completely adorable- though other might seeem to beg to differ- those incroyable smirks meant just for you.  point blank: hermione needs draco not ron- besides enemies have the best passion, am i right, *looks around, am i freaking right?...of course- Je suis (I am)- because they are peads in a pod, both tres intelligent. elizabeth/ jack- AGAIN- peads in a freaking pod. he said so himself.  . this has been in no way photo-copied. THAT RIGHT THERE should tell you something, m'dears. yes, i found the pic to prove mon peas in a pod theorem. YESSS!!!. yeah *calming down* . hehe

I was looking for layouts but then i saw someone who had them and it looked extremely yucky...no offence. besides i couldn't figure an inch of how to put the code in. myspace is so much easier but it bloody sucks so...i'm not even gonna compare- what's that?- i already did. oh well then. apologies.
